SQL: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_FieldID ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_FieldID.ConfID JOIN FieldID_Topic ON ConfID_FieldID.FieldID=FieldID_Topic.FieldID Where FieldID_Topic.Topic = 'Workshop On Parsing Technology' and ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue='Machine Translation'
